"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-gymnasts-use-chalk-olympics-21334017\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"If you are watching gymnastics at theOlympics, you can not help but notice that every competitor is using chalk.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For all gymnasts competing on bars, rings, pommel horse and even the balance beam, chalk is an essential part of the preparation moments before a routine.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chalk is undoubtedly messy to use, some commercial gyms have even banned it due to the extensive clean up required.\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But for elite gymnasts, chalk will remain a vital tool in the sport.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chalk is vital for gymnasts to ensure that they can maintain their strong grip.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The chalk helps absorb moisture on the hands and fingers, which eradicates the problem of sweaty palms and gymnasts losing their grip on the bar.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It also helps decrease friction which allows gymnasts to have a smooth spin during rotations.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Female gymnasts also apply chalk to their feet before a routine on the balance beam.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Male gymnasts also apply chalk on their armpits for the parallel bars as they swing with their upper arms.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Without chalk, there would be a drastic rise in falls.\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gymnastics chalk is made from Magnesium Carbonate (MgCO3).\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can typically be purchased as a powder, in a block or in liquid form, although that is usually more expensive.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is different to the chalk used in used in classrooms, which is made from\\u00a0Calcium Sulphate (CaSO4) and does not absorb moisture in the same way.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1298, \"end\": 1303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calcium_sulfate\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CaSO4\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calcium_sulfate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calcium_sulfate\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympics commentator wants to look away after 'tragic' moment for Brazil legend  ArrowMORE:The curious reason why swimmers slap themselves before a race at the Olympics  ArrowMORE:How Andy Murray and Dan Evans 'transformed' into Olympic medal contenders  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9678892428570633, \"rank\": 0.03241074302494659, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 1668, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9309287838919144e-21, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2045, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2349, \"entities\": []}]}"